2014-XX-XX - Version 0.4
 * Support for multi-line log messages
 * You can now choose the time separator to use. The default remains “:”.
 * Re-introduced the library for faster compilation of code using Einhard.
 * Support logging from multiple threads
 * Clang support

2011-11-10 - Version 0.3
 * Header-only implementation

2011-05-18 - Version 0.2
 * Coloured output when writing to a terminal
 * Suppress compilation of DEBUG and TRACE output if “NDEBUG” is defined.
 * Allow using Einhard in multiple source files.

2010-01-12 - Version 0.1:
 * Basic Logging
 * Supression of low relevance messages
 * Automatic addition of severity and timestamp

